doctype html
html
  head
    title Account Authentication Code
  body(
    style='background-color: #f3f4f6; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px'
  )
    div(style='max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px')
      div(
        style='background-color: white; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); padding: 24px'
      )
        h1(
          style='font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #1f2937; margin-bottom: 16px'
        ) Your Authentication Code
        p(style='color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 16px') Thank you for registering an account with us. To complete your registration, please use the following authentication code:

        div(
          style='background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center'
        )
          h2(
            style='font-size: 32px; font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 5px'
          )= authCode

        p(style='color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 16px') Please enter this code on the registration page to verify your email address and complete your account setup.

        p(style='color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 16px') This code will expire in 2 minutes for security reasons.

        p(style='color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 16px') If you did not request this authentication code, please ignore this email.

        p(style='color: #4b5563; margin-top: 24px') If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.

        p(style='color: #6b7280; margin-top: 16px') Best regards,
        p(style='color: #6b7280') The Account Management Team

    p(
      style='color: #9ca3af; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-top: 32px'
    ) This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.
